Invocation Name: my fairy tale
des: Play an interactive prince and princess-themed story with sound effects and prompts. Get ready for laughs and giggles as players fill in the blanks. At any point, you can say "Alexa, stop" to exit the skill. This skill was created using a Skill Blueprint. Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
